{
  "texts": [
    "A typical example targets the test oracle problem.",
    "A3Test [5] utilized a masked language modeling (MLM) objective to pre-train its model on over 188,000 method-assertion pairs.",
    "By learning to predict masked tokens within assertions, the model internalizes common assertion patterns.",
    "Compared to CAT-LM, its pre-training cost is significantly lower, requiring only 16 hours on a single RTX 3090.Multi-stage Foundational Learning.",
    "To construct a model proficient in both natural language and code, some methods adopt a multi-stage process."
  ]
}